            <p>According to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/croatia-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">Croatia Airlines Cancellation Policy</a>, passengers can cancel their flight 24 hours before the scheduled flight departure without paying any penalty. Croatia Airlines would provide a full refund if the booking was made a week before departure. There is no refund provided for reward tickets. </p>

